
In Seleuim there are 3 waits, which play very important rule for finding the web elements. 

	Thread.Sleep(10000);


  1. Implicit wait : Implicite wait is command, when called, it will wait for the visibility of all elements for the web page. 
  
    
  
  
  
  2.Explicit wait: Explicit wait is command, when called, it will wait for the visibility of specific elements or specific condition. 
  
  
  
  
  
  3. Fluent wait:  every  3 seconds refresh the elements till 30 seconds unless the specific element is visible. 
  
  
  3 * 30 = 10 times 
  
  


